data.description: Enjoy peaceful, country living in this 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home.  This sprawling two story home has room for everyone.  A large living room with a wood burning stove, kitchen with plenty of storage, cedar lined closet upstairs, a master suite with double vanity, and so much more.  Spend your evenings on your back deck with retractable awnings, looking out over a private yard with no neighbors in sight.  A small barn has 3 stalls for horses.
